text: Tulli is a surname. Notable people with the surname include: * Alessandro Tulli (born 1982), Italian footballer * Frank Tulli (born 1944), American former Republican member of the Pennsylvania House of Representatives * Giacomo Tulli (born 1987), Italian footballer * Magdalena Tulli (born 1955), Polish novelist * Marco Tulli (1920–1982), Italian character actor * Vincent Tulli (born 1966, French sound mixer and sound designer == See also == * Tuļļi Lum, Estonian/Livonian folk music band * Tulli Papyrus, document of questionable origins that some have interpreted as evidence of ancient flying saucers * Tullis, a surname and given name
title: Tulli
